{"title":"hexo","uid":"45b05c0adc7d6b51711d3e13e977b9ba","slug":"hexo","date":"2024-01-28T08:31:17.000Z","updated":"2024-01-28T08:31:17.000Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/hexo.json","keywords":null,"cover":null,"content":"<p>使用<a href=\"https://github.com/auroral-ui/hexo-theme-aurora\">hexo-theme-aurora</a>主题搭建自己的github博客网站。</p>\n<h1 id=\"版本\"><a href=\"#版本\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"版本\"></a>版本</h1><ul>\n<li>hexo: ^6.3.0</li>\n<li>hexo-theme-aurora: ^2.5.3</li>\n<li>hexo-plugin-aurora: ^1.8.4</li>\n</ul>\n<h1 id=\"引用图片\"><a href=\"#引用图片\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"引用图片\"></a>引用图片</h1><ol>\n<li><p>修改 <code>_config.yml</code></p>\n <figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">post_asset_folder: true</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n<li><p>保存图片</p>\n<p> 修改完配置后，<code>hexo new &lt;post&gt;</code> 后会在文章的同级目录生成一个和文章名相同的文件夹，将图片存入该文件夹</p>\n <figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">source</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t_posts</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\tpost1</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\tpost1.md</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n<li><p>插入图片</p>\n <figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">&#123;% asset_img [image] [title] %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>\n</ol>\n<h1 id=\"智能机器人\"><a href=\"#智能机器人\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"智能机器人\"></a><a href=\"https://aurora.tridiamond.tech/en/configs/plugins.html#bot-dia\">智能机器人</a></h1><p>打开机器人，修改 <code>_config.aurora.yml</code></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">aurora_bot:</span><br><span class=\"line\">  enable: true  # 打开</span><br><span class=\"line\">  locale: zh-CN  # 语言</span><br><span class=\"line\">  bot_type: dia</span><br><span class=\"line\">  tips:</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h1 id=\"设置网站favicon\"><a href=\"#设置网站favicon\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"设置网站favicon\"></a>设置网站favicon</h1><p>修改<code>_config.aurora.yml</code></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">site_meta:</span><br><span class=\"line\">  cdn: cn</span><br><span class=\"line\">  favicon: &lt;favicon&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h1 id=\"description换行\"><a href=\"#description换行\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"description换行\"></a>description换行</h1><figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">site:</span><br><span class=\"line\">  description: &quot;Wait for the wind or chase after it.\\&lt;br\\&gt;等风来还是追风去。&quot;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h1 id=\"开启busuanzi\"><a href=\"#开启busuanzi\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"开启busuanzi\"></a>开启busuanzi</h1><p>修改<code>_config.aurora.yml</code></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">busuanzi:</span><br><span class=\"line\">  enable: true</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>","text":"使用hexo-theme-aurora主题搭建自己的github博客网站。 版本 hexo: ^6.3.0 hexo-theme-aurora: ^2.5.3 ...","permalink":"/post/hexo","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":670,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"hexo","slug":"hexo","count":1,"path":"api/categories/hexo.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"hexo","slug":"hexo","count":1,"path":"api/tags/hexo.json"},{"name":"hexo-theme-aurora","slug":"hexo-theme-aurora","count":1,"path":"api/tags/hexo-theme-aurora.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E7%89%88%E6%9C%AC\"><span class=\"toc-text\">版本</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%BC%95%E7%94%A8%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%87\"><span class=\"toc-text\">引用图片</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%99%BA%E8%83%BD%E6%9C%BA%E5%99%A8%E4%BA%BA\"><span class=\"toc-text\">智能机器人</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AE%E7%BD%91%E7%AB%99favicon\"><span class=\"toc-text\">设置网站favicon</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#description%E6%8D%A2%E8%A1%8C\"><span class=\"toc-text\">description换行</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%BC%80%E5%90%AFbusuanzi\"><span class=\"toc-text\">开启busuanzi</span></a></li></ol>","author":{"name":"Rey","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/41515641?v=4","link":"/","description":"Wait for the wind or chase after it.<br>等风来还是追风去。","socials":{"github":{"icon":"fat fa-github","link":"https://github.com/czp-first"},"twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}},"mapped":true,"hidden":false,"prev_post":{"title":"JWT简介","uid":"2313231ee754c6e54c611ddd3e585900","slug":"JWT简介","date":"2024-01-31T03:13:42.000Z","updated":"2024-01-31T03:13:42.000Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/JWT简介.json","keywords":null,"cover":[],"text":"什么